headline: Morgan Stanley Private Credit Leads Strategic Growth Capital Investment in Fetch
summary: NEW YORK, September 16, 2025--Morgan Stanley Private Credit announced today that it has led an incremental senior debt financing for Fetch, America's Rewards App, upsizing the existing debt facility to $110 million aggregate. Morgan Stanley Private Credit initially provided debt financing to Fetch in March 2024.
